RMBlast license notice
======================

The official RMBlast download page states that RMBlast is licensed under the
Open Source License version 2.1.

SPDX-License-Identifier: OSL-2.1

The pre-built RMBlast package also includes the following NCBI public domain
notice in LICENSE.rmblast for bundled BLAST+ components:

